attributes.comment: Can be used as framebuffer color attachment

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_STORAGE_IMAGE_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used for storage images (STORAGE_IMAGE descriptor type)

attributes.comment: Format supports atomic operations in case it is used for storage images

attributes.comment: Format can be used for storage texel buffers (IBOs)

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_STORAGE_TEXEL_BUFFER_ATOMIC_BIT
attributes.comment: Format supports atomic operations in case it is used for storage texel buffers

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_VERTEX_BUFFER_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used for vertex buffers (VBOs)

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_COLOR_ATTACHMENT_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used for color attachment images

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_COLOR_ATTACHMENT_BLEND_BIT
attributes.comment: Format supports blending in case it is used for color attachment images

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_DEPTH_STENCIL_ATTACHMENT_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used for depth/stencil attachment images

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_BLIT_DST_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used as the destination image of blits with vkCmdBlitImage

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_SAMPLED_IMAGE_FILTER_CUBIC_BIT_IMG

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_TRANSFER_DST_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used as the destination image of image transfer commands

attributes.comment: Format can have different chroma, min and mag filters

attributes.comment: Format can have cosited rather than midpoint chroma samples

attributes.name: VK_FORMAT_FEATURE_SAMPLED_IMAGE_FILTER_MINMAX_BIT
attributes.comment: Format can be used with min/max reduction filtering

attributes.name: VK_PIPELINE_STAGE_CONDITIONAL_RENDERING_BIT_EXT

attributes.comment: Command buffers may release their memory individually

attributes.name: VK_COMMAND_POOL_CREATE_PROTECTED_BIT
attributes.comment: Command buffers allocated from pool are protected command buffers

attributes.comment: Release resources owned by the buffer

attributes.name: VK_ATTACHMENT_DESCRIPTION_MAY_ALIAS_BIT

attributes.name: VK_DESCRIPTOR_POOL_CREATE_FREE_DESCRIPTOR_SET_BIT
